    "m_Type": "UnityEditor.ShaderGraph.StickyNoteData",
    "m_ObjectId": "5b35c3c0dbe24ad4b3975c7fe313f879",
    "m_Title": "Upstream corrections and efficiency",
    "m_Content": "Most of the computation is done on shader compile-time and therefore, done once, ahead of time.\n\nUVs corrections have to be done first to compensate the skewed end-result of the hexagonal grid's computations.",
